HEADWORD: Pericambium
<hw>Per`i*cam"bi*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Peri-</er>, and <er>Cambium</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>A
